---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Resources">
  <h1>Resources</h1>

  <p>Curated knowledge and references I've found useful.</p>

  <h2>domain investing</h2>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>NameBio</strong> — Domain sales database and market research.</li>
    <li><strong>ExpiredDomains.net</strong> — Daily domain drop lists and filtering.</li>
    <li><strong>Afternic</strong> — Domain listing and marketplace.</li>
    <li><strong>GoDaddy Auctions</strong> — Expired domain auctions.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>freelance & development</h2>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Next.js</strong> — React framework for production web apps.</li>
    <li><strong>Supabase</strong> — Open-source Firebase alternative.</li>
    <li><strong>Astro</strong> — Content-first web framework (this site runs on it).</li>
    <li><strong>Flutter</strong> — Cross-platform mobile development.</li>
    <li><strong>Mostaql</strong> — Arab world freelance platform.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>sales & outreach</h2>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Brevo</strong> — Transactional email (300 free/day).</li>
    <li><strong>Resend</strong> — Email API for developers (100 free/day).</li>
    <li><strong>Mailgun</strong> — Email service for outbound (100 free/day).</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>datasets</h2>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Domain Sales DB</strong> — 19K+ domain sales records for comparable analysis.</li>
    <li><strong>OpenStreetMap</strong> — Free business location data for lead generation.</li>
  </ul>
</Layout>
